('Ashardalon, the Ancient Red', 'Gargantuan', 'Dragon', 'Chaotic Evil', '26', 90000, 22, NULL, 546, '28d20+252', 40, NULL, NULL, 30, 10, 29, 20, 17, 25, '{"fire"}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{"blindsight": 60, "darkvision": 120, "passive Perception": 17}', '{"Common", "Draconic", "Infernal"}', 'A legendary ancient red dragon who made a pact with a pit fiend, replacing his own heart with that of a demon. He is among the most powerful dragons in existence, ruling a network of volcano Gates.', 'Ashardalon is a unique dragon who achieved near-immortality through dark pacts. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that even the Shadow Monarch cannot truly destroy him. His demonic heart makes him nearly invincible.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"dragon", "fire", "ancient", "named", "demon-heart"}'),
('Chardalyn Dragon', 'Huge', 'Construct', 'Chaotic Evil', '11', 7200, 19, NULL, 200, '16d12+96', 40, NULL, NULL, 23, 10, 22, 10, 13, 16, '{"cold", "fire", "lightning", "poison"}', '{"charmed", "exhaustion", "frightened", "paralyzed", "petrified", "poisoned"}', '{}', '{}', '{"blindsight": 60, "darkvision": 120, "passive Perception": 13}', '{"understands the languages of its creator but cannot speak"}', 'A construct dragon made from chardalyn, a magical crystal that corrupts those who touch it. It breathes freezing cold and spreads corruption wherever it goes.', 'The Chardalyn Dragon is a unique construct created by dark mages. In the post-reset world, it has become more dangerous as chardalyn corruption spreads through certain Gate types. It serves as a warning of the dangers of unchecked magical experimentation.', 'A', true, 'MM', '{"construct", "dragon", "cold", "named", "corruption"}'),
('Dracolich', 'Gargantuan', 'Undead', 'Chaotic Evil', '17', 18000, 19, NULL, 256, '19d12+133', 40, NULL, NULL, 27, 10, 25, 20, 15, 19, '{"necrotic"}', '{"poison"}', '{"radiant"}', '{"charmed", "exhaustion", "frightened", "paralyzed", "poisoned"}', '{"blindsight": 60, "darkvision": 120, "passive Perception": 15}', '{"Common", "Draconic"}', 'An undead dragon who achieved immortality by binding its soul to a phylactery. It combines the power of a dragon with the resilience of undeath, making it nearly impossible to destroy permanently.', 'Dracoliches are dragons who have achieved lichdom. They are among the most feared undead in Gates. In the post-reset world, they have become more common as dragons seek immortality. Their phylacteries must be destroyed to truly defeat them.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"undead", "dragon", "lich", "named", "immortal", "phylactery"}'),

