('Demogorgon, Prince of Demons', 'Gargantuan', 'Fiend', 'Chaotic Evil', '26', 90000, 22, NULL, 406, '28d20+224', 50, NULL, 50, 29, 14, 26, 20, 18, 24, '{"cold", "fire", "lightning"}', '{"poison"}', '{"radiant"}', '{"charmed", "frightened", "poisoned"}', '{"truesight": 120, "passive Perception": 18}', '{"Abyssal", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'The most powerful demon prince, with two heads that think independently. He commands legions of demons and seeks to corrupt all of creation. His mere presence can drive mortals insane.', 'Demogorgon is the Prince of Demons, the most powerful of all demon lords. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that chaos and corruption are the true nature of existence. Only the Shadow Monarch himself could truly defeat him.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"fiend", "demon", "prince", "named", "two-headed", "insanity"}'),
('Orcus, Prince of Undeath', 'Gargantuan', 'Fiend', 'Chaotic Evil', '26', 90000, 20, NULL, 405, '27d20+189', 40, NULL, NULL, 27, 14, 24, 20, 17, 25, '{"cold", "fire", "lightning"}', '{"poison"}', '{"radiant"}', '{"charmed", "frightened", "poisoned"}', '{"truesight": 120, "passive Perception": 17}', '{"Abyssal", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'A demon prince who commands all undead. He wields the Wand of Orcus, a legendary artifact that can raise the dead and command legions of undead. He seeks to transform all life into undeath.', 'Orcus is the Prince of Undeath, commanding all undead creatures. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that death and undeath are the true nature of existence. His wand is one of the most powerful artifacts in existence.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"fiend", "demon", "prince", "named", "undeath", "wand"}'),
('Asmodeus, Lord of the Nine Hells', 'Large', 'Fiend', 'Lawful Evil', '30', 155000, 21, NULL, 666, '36d10+468', 30, NULL, NULL, 29, 17, 26, 30, 24, 28, '{"cold", "fire", "poison"}', '{"bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from nonmagical attacks"}', '{}', '{"charmed", "exhaustion", "frightened", "poisoned"}', '{"truesight": 120, "passive Perception": 24}', '{"all", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'The absolute ruler of the Nine Hells and the most powerful devil in existence. He commands all devils and seeks to corrupt all souls. His power rivals that of the Supreme Deity himself.', 'Asmodeus is the Lord of the Nine Hells, the absolute ruler of all devils. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that order through tyranny is superior to chaos. His power is such that even the Shadow Monarch must take him seriously as a threat.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"fiend", "devil", "lord", "named", "nine-hells", "archfiend"}'),

