('Acererak, the Demilich', 'Tiny', 'Undead', 'Neutral Evil', '21', 33000, 20, NULL, 80, '32d4', 0, NULL, NULL, 1, 20, 10, 20, 20, 20, '{"bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from nonmagical attacks"}', '{"cold", "fire", "lightning", "necrotic", "poison", "psychic"}', '{"radiant"}', '{"charmed", "exhaustion", "frightened", "paralyzed", "petrified", "poisoned"}', '{"truesight": 120, "passive Perception": 20}', '{"Common plus up to five other languages", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'A legendary lich who has transcended even lichdom, becoming a demilich. Only his skull remains, but he is more powerful than ever. He can trap souls and command legions of undead.', 'Acererak is a unique lich who has achieved demilichdom, transcending even normal lichdom. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that true immortality comes from transcending all forms of existence. His skull is one of the most powerful artifacts in existence.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"undead", "lich", "demilich", "named", "immortal", "skull"}'),
('Vecna, the Archlich', 'Medium', 'Undead', 'Neutral Evil', '26', 90000, 20, NULL, 272, '32d8+128', 30, NULL, NULL, 10, 16, 18, 20, 19, 24, '{"cold", "lightning", "necrotic"}', '{"poison"}', '{"radiant"}', '{"charmed", "exhaustion", "frightened", "paralyzed", "poisoned"}', '{"truesight": 120, "passive Perception": 19}', '{"all", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'A legendary archlich who achieved godhood through dark rituals. He wields the Hand and Eye of Vecna, legendary artifacts that grant incredible power. He seeks to become the supreme ruler of all existence.', 'Vecna is a unique archlich who achieved godhood. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that he is the true god of secrets and undeath. His Hand and Eye are among the most powerful artifacts in existence, rivaling even the Supreme Deity''s power.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"undead", "lich", "archlich", "named", "god", "hand-of-vecna", "eye-of-vecna"}'),

