('Ogremoch, Prince of Evil Earth', 'Huge', 'Elemental', 'Lawful Evil', '20', 25000, 18, NULL, 526, '31d12+341', 30, NULL, NULL, 30, 8, 28, 12, 15, 18, '{"bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from nonmagical attacks"}', '{"poison"}', '{}', '{"exhaustion", "paralyzed", "petrified", "poisoned", "unconscious"}', '{"darkvision": 120, "tremorsense": 120, "passive Perception": 15}', '{"Terran", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'The Prince of Evil Earth, a massive earth elemental who commands all earth elementals. He seeks to crush all of creation and transform the world into a realm of stone and dust.', 'Ogremoch is the Prince of Evil Earth, commanding all earth elementals. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that stone and permanence are the true nature of existence. He rules underground Gates with absolute power.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"elemental", "earth", "prince", "named", "evil-earth"}'),
('Olhydra, Princess of Evil Water', 'Huge', 'Elemental', 'Chaotic Evil', '18', 20000, 17, NULL, 324, '24d12+168', 50, NULL, 150, 24, 20, 24, 18, 17, 20, '{"bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from nonmagical attacks"}', '{"acid", "fire", "poison"}', '{}', '{"exhaustion", "grappled", "paralyzed", "petrified", "poisoned", "prone", "restrained", "unconscious"}', '{"darkvision": 120, "passive Perception": 17}', '{"Aquan", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'The Princess of Evil Water, a massive water elemental who commands all water elementals. She seeks to drown all of creation and transform the world into a realm of eternal ocean.', 'Olhydra is the Princess of Evil Water, commanding all water elementals. In the post-reset world, she challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that water and change are the true nature of existence. She rules ocean Gates with absolute power.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"elemental", "water", "princess", "named", "evil-water"}'),
('Yan-C-Bin, Prince of Evil Air', 'Huge', 'Elemental', 'Neutral Evil', '18', 20000, 19, NULL, 363, '22d12+220', 0, NULL, NULL, 24, 24, 26, 16, 17, 20, '{"bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from nonmagical attacks"}', '{"lightning", "thunder", "poison"}', '{}', '{"exhaustion", "grappled", "paralyzed", "petrified", "poisoned", "prone", "restrained", "unconscious"}', '{"darkvision": 120, "passive Perception": 17}', '{"Auran", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'The Prince of Evil Air, a massive air elemental who commands all air elementals. He seeks to scatter all of creation and transform the world into a realm of eternal wind.', 'Yan-C-Bin is the Prince of Evil Air, commanding all air elementals. In the post-reset world, he challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that air and freedom are the true nature of existence. He rules sky Gates with absolute power.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"elemental", "air", "prince", "named", "evil-air"}'),

