('Atropus, the World Born Dead', 'Gargantuan', 'Undead', 'Neutral Evil', '30', 155000, 25, NULL, 900, '40d20+480', 60, NULL, NULL, 30, 11, 30, 3, 11, 11, '{"bludgeoning, piercing, slashing from nonmagical attacks"}', '{"cold", "necrotic", "poison"}', '{"radiant"}', '{"charmed", "exhaustion", "frightened", "paralyzed", "poisoned"}', '{"blindsight": 120, "passive Perception": 11}', '{"telepathy 120 ft."}', 'A massive undead moon that orbits the world, spreading death and undeath wherever it passes. It is a living world that died and now seeks to kill all other worlds.', 'Atropus is the World Born Dead, a unique undead entity that is an entire world that died and became undead. In the post-reset world, it challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that death and undeath are the true nature of all existence. Only the Shadow Monarch himself could truly defeat it.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"undead", "monstrosity", "world", "named", "moon", "world-ending"}'),

