('Zariel, the Fallen Angel', 'Large', 'Fiend', 'Lawful Evil', '26', 90000, 21, NULL, 580, '40d10+360', 30, NULL, NULL, 27, 22, 28, 26, 24, 26, '{"cold"}', '{"fire", "poison"}', '{}', '{"poisoned", "charmed", "frightened"}', '{"truesight": 120, "passive Perception": 24}', '{"all", "telepathy 120 ft."}', 'A fallen angel who was once a celestial but fell from grace and became an archdevil. She commands the armies of Avernus, the first layer of hell, and seeks to corrupt all of creation.', 'Zariel is a unique being who was once a celestial but fell from grace. In the post-reset world, she challenges the Supreme Deity''s authority, claiming that her fall proves that even the highest beings can be corrupted. She serves as a warning of the dangers of pride and ambition.', 'S', true, 'MM', '{"fiend", "devil", "fallen-angel", "named", "archdevil", "avernus"}'),

